<p><i><b>Blue Hill Avenue</b></i> is a 2001 American <a href="/wiki/Crime_film" title="Crime film">crime film</a> directed and written by <a href="/wiki/Craig_Ross,_Jr." title="Craig Ross, Jr.">Craig Ross, Jr.</a>, and starring <a href="/wiki/Allen_Payne" title="Allen Payne">Allen Payne</a>. Ross Jr. also edited and executive produced the film.</p>
<p></p>
